*note, latest gimp 2.8.20 has a transform cage/ rotate bug, use command below to install its snapped version*

sudo apt install snapd
sudo snap install gimp
snap run gimp

To prevent resolution lost:
1. Rotate tool: Interpolation - none
2. Free select tool: Antiliasing - unselect

To trim:
1. Free select tool
2. Move tool: to select wanted area
3. Add alpha channel (under layers, right side of app)
4. Select > Invert
5. Cltrl x to delete unwanted parts

To change canvas size:
Image > Canvas size> 10000 by 10000 for 10x to 10n

# Gimp stitching

. Adjustment for yaw
. Clean up blind spot/ define features
. Combine map